{"tid":1390873,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我知大家好想幫捐錢幫手, 但親自行出黎先係最幫到手","createTime":"2019-07-31T09:04:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T09:34:47.000Z","uid":131731,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"79e1afba0dbbbfc21205c393d66f0bdb10131e83","tid":1390873,"uid":131731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T09:04:59.000Z","msg":"當然出到錢嘅就出錢, 出到力嘅就出力<br />\n兄弟爬山, 各有各做<br />\n但我唔希望因為噉而變咗捐錢活動, 好似捐咗錢就盡哂力噉, 變相連和理非都少咗人出黎<br />\n近日亦有好多手足被捕同埋控告暴動罪, 唔多唔少都會有人嚇怕, 更加想捐咗錢就算<br />\n<br />\n我衷心希望香港人唔好咁善忘, 每一次嘅抗爭都要勇敢企出黎<br />\n即使唔係最前線都係幫助好大<br />\n就係因為大家都出盡每一分力, 先有今日嘅局面<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港, 時代革命</span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"dfa88e3f8e85ef214c1d06671d6d6defca9a47a8","tid":1390873,"uid":110851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T09:05:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/VfuWZd5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVfuWZd5.png&h=4576ca37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1cSQ2oL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1cSQ2oL.png&h=cef8ee5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VkT1vED.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVkT1vED.png&h=0accd33f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"c8fdd06c44de6ce2f0d3d02d4bfc08123051f3fb","tid":1390873,"uid":131731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T09:05:35.000Z","msg":"諗唔到post咩台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23acec050e1098e59a1999d1fbb46a8